<p>Sympathetic to JVC’s views on Franco-Prussian war [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">7332</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Astonished at JVC’s readiness to begin work. Will send sheets as soon as possible. Has asked Murray to charge for stereotypes of 64 woodblocks at cost. JVC must make his own agreement with publisher.</p>
