        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the relationship between this letter and the <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7332.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. V. Carus, 2 October 1870</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7332.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. V. Carus, 2 October 1870</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">Carus was to translate <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> into German; the publisher of Carus trans. 1871 was E. Schweizerbart’sche Verlagshandlung (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7332.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. V. Carus, 2 October 1870</ref> and n. 4).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">CD’s letter to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_978.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">William Clowes</ref>, the printer of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref>, has not been found.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f5">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7327.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to John Murray, 26 September 1870</ref>.</note>
